biz.neustar.hopper.record
Class RRset

java.lang.Object
  biz.neustar.hopper.record.RRset
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class RRset
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

A set of Records with the same name, type, and class. Also included are all RRSIG records signing the data records.

Author:
Brian Wellington
See Also:
Record, RRSIGRecord, Serialized Form
